Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.modelview

Reduced versions of model classes that are used by the clients and sent over the network.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    BoardProductionView
    Board production, always turns two jolly into one jolly.
    DepotView
    View equivalent of a depot.
    DevelopmentCardSlotView
    View equivalent to the development slot class.
    DevMarketView
    View equivalent of the development card market.
    FaithTrackView
    View equivalent of the faith track.
    GameView
    Singleton class that is the view equivalent of the Game class.
    MarketView
    View equivalent to the market class.
    MatchSettings
    Holds various settings related to the client an to the current game.
    PlayerView
    Contains all the views related to one player.
    SlotView
    View equivalent to the slot class.
    SpecialProductionView
    View equivalent to special production.
    StrongboxView
    View equivalent to the strongbox class.
